   525→
   526→## Summary
   527→
   528→| Atom | Status | Action |
   529→|------|--------|--------|
   530→| `Typography` | ✅ v1 exists | No work needed |
   531→| `Link` | ✅ v1 exists | No work needed |
   532→| `Box` | ✅ v1 exists | No work needed |
   533→| `ImageWrapper` | — | Not needed; inline `<div>` layout inside card |
   534→| `Carousel` | v0 only (MUI) | New v1 (keen-slider, no MUI) |
   535→| `RecommendationsProductCard` | v0 only (MUI) | New v1 from catalog `RelatedProductCard` |
   536→| `FavoriteButton` | catalog only | New v1 presentational atom; state stays in catalog |
   537→| `Tooltip` | v0 only (MUI) | New v1 (`@floating-ui/react`) |
   538→| `Popover` | v0 only (MUI) | New v1 (`@floating-ui/react`) |
   539→| `TrendingProductsWidget` | catalog only | New widget in `packages/react/src/widgets/` |
   540→| `useTrendingProducts` | new | App-agnostic hook with `fetcher` injection |
   541→
   542→**Delivery order** (by dependency):
   543→1. `Tooltip`
   544→2. `Popover`
   545→3. `FavoriteButton` (uses Tooltip)
   546→4. `Carousel`
   547→5. `RecommendationsProductCard` (uses Popover for prices)
   548→6. `useTrendingProducts` hook
   549→7. `TrendingProductsWidget` (assembles all)

